creator: Amber Car Services Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the Amber Cars booking App!
Through this app you can:
• Order a taxi
• Cancel a booking
• Track the vehicle on the map as it makes its way towards you!
• Receive real-time notifications of the status of your taxi
• Pay by cash or with card
• To order a taxi for an exact pick-up time
descriptionShort: Welcome to the Amber Cars booking App!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Latest Passenger App with brand new redesign and features
